data.description: Better than new construction, this stunning home is welcoming & cozy feeling! Situated in Grays Creek w/ an easy drive to Hope Mills, Fayetteville, & Ft Liberty (32 minutes to center)! This spacious home offers an open floor plan, large formal dining, custom plantation shutters, primary suite, & laundry space on the main level. One of my favorite spaces in this home is the kitchen w/ a huge island, granite counters, & a walk-in pantry! The primary suite boasts ample space for your furniture & a sitting area where you can relax & watch the hummingbirds at the feeder. The 2nd floor features 3 guest bdrms, walk-in closets, 2 full baths, a loft for additional entertaining space, & the most cozy flex/office/reading space! The backyard is gorgeous w/ mature trees & landscaping, rear fencing, & a screened patio for relaxing in the evenings or early morning enjoying a nice cup of coffee! Watching the gorgeous sunsets on the front porch is one of the seller's favorite things about this home!
